---
// FutureFeatures.astro - Upcoming features roadmap
---

<section class="future-features">
    <h2 class="section-title">New Features Coming Soon</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">What we're working on next</p>

    <div class="features-list">
        <div class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-status in-progress">In Progress</span>
            <h3 class="feature-name">MacOS Seqoia Support</h3>
            <p class="feature-desc">Currently only works on MacOS 26 Tahoe.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-status planned">Planned</span>
            <h3 class="feature-name">Better Command Palette</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-status planned">Planned</span>
            <h3 class="feature-name">Improved AI Sidebar</h3>
        </div>
        <h2 class="section-subtitle">and many more..</h2>
        <h2 class="section-subtitle">
            Logia was build as a personal tool,to complement my own workflow.
            There are still a lot of issues and is still in Beta.<br />ALso i do
            not have a Mac to test so the MacOS version can be unstable.
        </h2>
        <h2 class="section-subtitle">Thanks for using Logia ;)</h2>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .future-features {
        padding: 6rem 2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
        text-align: center;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
    }

    .features-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        border-radius: 12px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .feature-status {
        padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .feature-status.planned {
        background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
        color: #a5b4fc;
    }

    .feature-status.in-progress {
        background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
        color: #86efac;
    }

    .feature-name {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        min-width: 140px;
    }

    .feature-desc {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin: 0;
        flex: 1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .future-features {
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
        }

        .feature-item {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .feature-name {
            min-width: auto;
        }
    }
</style>
